get.description:
Returns the current user's information.

Args:
    current_user: The current user as a CurrentUser object.

Returns:
    The current user as a User object.

Raises:
    HTTPException: If the current user is not authenticated.

post.description:
Creates a new project folder.

Args:
    folder: The project folder to create.
    db: The database session.
    user: The current user.

Returns:
    The created project folder.

Raises:
    HTTPException: If the project folder is not found.

patch.description:
Updates a project folder.

Args:
    id: The id of the project folder to update.
    folder: The updated project folder.
    db: The database session.
    user: The current user.

Raises:
    HTTPException: If the project folder is not found or if the user is not allowed to update the project folder.

delete.description:
Deletes a project folder.

Args:
    id (int): The ID of the project folder to delete.
    db (SessionDep): The database session.
    user (CurrentUser): The current user.

Raises:
    HTTPException: If the project folder is not found or if the current user is not allowed to delete it.

Returns:
    dict: A response with a message indicating that the project folder was deleted.
